{"tid":2496575,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"15歲男生被控去年6.12一周年旺角堵路 還柙3周後陳慧敏今判處160小時社會服務令","createTime":"2021-04-20T02:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T02:49:09.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9f9cb19106c1ce7726eab2f146e693994f879081","tid":2496575,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T02:27:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15128\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15128&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuG8KfKULefuOMk0AcQ9dAAw%3D&h=383d23cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15128</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第二庭<br />\n#陳慧敏裁判官<br />\n#20200612旺角 #判刑<br />\n#公眾妨擾罪 #阻街<br />\n<br />\nD2: 15歲手足<br />\n<br />\n控罪：在公眾地方犯的妨擾罪<br />\n第228章 《簡易程序治罪條例》第4(28)條<br />\n被控於2020年6月12日，在旺角砵蘭街與山東街交界外與其他不知名人士堵塞馬路，因而可導致該處交通遭受阻礙。<br />\n<br />\n背景：<br />\n2020年6月12日為反送中抗爭首次大型衝突「6.12」一周年。警方阻撓市民在添馬公園舉行集會，當日晚上有市民在旺角街頭合唱《願榮光歸香港》，卻遭警方驅散。案件於2020年12月7日首度提堂，３名被告原面對一項非法集結罪，#王詩麗裁判官 批准D1及D2保釋候訊。D3於3月12日認罪，4月1日連同另一宗案件判監７個月。D2在3月30日在 #陳慧敏裁判官 面前承認較輕的妨擾罪，還押至今判刑。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n📌 上次答辯及求情<br />\n<br />\n速報：160小時社會服務令🛑"},{"pid":"23aa88144ba9804bebb86b36b7683f86d94864e3","tid":2496575,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T02:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939bfa37e48a3b1dc388cda6ff87ac200f26f2c8","tid":2496575,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23aa88144ba9804bebb86b36b7683f86d94864e3","tid":2496575,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T02:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mo